payload.text:
Generate the report in HTML with print-safe CSS. Use these rules:

page-break-inside: avoid;

page-break-before: auto;

page-break-after: auto;

For images: max-width: 100%; page-break-inside: avoid;

Keep headings, text, and images together in blocks.

Ensure that printing the HTML or exporting it to PDF will not split any text or image across pages.
